<title>
DTC P0557 / P0558
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1104071001">
<title>
DTC Detecting Condition and Trouble Area
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.663in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.534in"/>
<thead valign = "middle">
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" align = "center">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0557: Brake Booster Pressure Sensor Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Although difference between intake manifold pressure and barometric pressure exceeds specified value, brake booster switch is kept ON for more than 3 sec.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Brake booster switch (brake booster) and/or its circuit)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
P0558: Brake Booster Pressure Sensor Circuit High
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
A state which difference between intake manifold pressure and barometric pressure is below specified value is detected more than 3 times while applying brake at vehicle speed 10 km/h (6 mile/h) or more.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
